<sect1 id="ESDL_Attributes_max_count_var">
  <!-- DNT-Start --><title>max_count_var</title><!-- DNT-End -->

  <para><indexterm>
      <primary>max_count_var</primary>
    </indexterm>The max_count_var attribute is used to specify the expected
  max items in a dataset (ESParray).</para>

  <para><emphasis role="bold">Example:</emphasis></para>

  <!-- DNT-Start --><programlisting>[max_count_var("iesp.Constants.JD.MaxRecords")] ESParray &lt;ESPstruct MYRecord, Record&gt; Records;   </programlisting><!-- DNT-End -->

  <para>Roxie will define the constant iesp.Constants.<!-- DNT-Start -->JD<!-- DNT-End -->.MaxRecords and change
  it at will without affecting <!-- DNT-Start -->ESP<!-- DNT-End -->.</para>
</sect1>
